Name: Othello Let's Go
About the game: Othello (Reversi) Let's Go is a highly-acclaimed strategy board game for all ages. It takes a minute to learn and a lifetime to master! Four different game modes are available for you to play: Classic Solo World class AI with 8 difficulty levels, suits for both beginners and advanced players. Endgame Challenge Solve 80 carefully selected endgame puzzles. Give it a try and show yourself you are a truly Othello master. Lights Out Classic electronic game, Lights Out. Can you flip all pieces to black on the board? Local co-op for Two Players Do play with your family and friends!
